original_title: Ayako Ishikawa - The Premium Live Anime Classic
overview: Recorded at Ebisu Garden Hall on December 27, 2015 to celebrate the release of Ayako Ishikawa's major debut album "ANIME CLASSIC". The tickets were sold out immediately and it was a premium live performance. The album includes all the songs from "ANIME CLASSIC," as well as movie music, Vocaloid covers, classic classical songs, Ayako Ishikawa's original songs, and more.
title: Ayako Ishikawa - The Premium Live Anime Classic
